        "action": "Remove the criteria for men who have sex with men to wait before donating blood",
        "additional_details": "",
        "background": "Currently, men are not permitted to donate blood if they have had sex with another man in the last 3 months.\r\n\r\nWe would like the government to remove this restriction and allow men who have sex with men the same privilege to donate blood as everybody else.",
